                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">üîÑ</div>
                    <h4>Real-time Updates</h4>
                    <p>Get real-time processing status and updates as your content is being generated and optimized.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">üì±</div>
                    <h4>Mobile Optimized</h4>
                    <p>Responsive design and mobile-first approach for seamless experience across all devices.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

